                        p Team Treehouse is a paid service, it's $25 a month. I highly reccomend it to begginers and advanced developers. They have a very well structured learning system that will show you the ins and outs of any language or paltform you'd like to learn.
                        a(href='http://referrals.trhou.se/alexanderalegre', target='_blank') 7 Day Free Trial!
                .media
                    .media-left
                        a(href='#')
                            img.img-rounded.media-object(src='/images/htmlcss.png' alt='html and css')
                    .media-body
                        h4.media-heading HTML &amp; CSS
                        p HTML and CSS go hand in hand. You need to use both in order to render a website's content and to style that content.
                        a(href='http://learn.shayhowe.com/', target='_blank') Shay Howe's Free Guide
